def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if hx : x > 0 then
    Finset.max' (Finset.filter (λ d : ℕ, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) (Finset.range (x + 1)))
      (by simp [hx])
  else 1
∀ (x : ℕ), x ≠ 0 → δ x = Nat.greatestOddDivisor x

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : 0 < x then
    Nat.find_greatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x
  else 0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : 0 < x then
    Nat.find_greatest (fun d => odd d ∧ d ∣ x) x
  else
    0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x ≠ 0 then
    Nat.find_greatest (λ d, d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x
  else
    0

def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if x = 0 then 0 else Nat.findGreatest (fun d => d ∣ x ∧ d % 2 = 1) x
